borrow one from a friend,

00:05:12.100 --> 00:05:13.930
whose name I still remember, David.

00:05:13.930 --> 00:05:19.020
And came home and I grew up
in communist Czechoslovakia

00:05:19.020 --> 00:05:21.450
where you had all these
Russian movies

00:05:21.450 --> 00:05:26.480
