a gun, plastic one or real.

00:06:02.710 --> 00:06:07.000
And I realized there is something
in the past of my grandfather

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:14.560
that it's strange, it's
not completely normal.

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:20.710 position:56%
