00:51:35.160 --> 00:51:39.910
And they went out with the Polish
village girls and the transports

00:51:39.910 --> 00:51:42.980
from Czech, they were
rich transports,

00:51:42.980 --> 00:51:46.700
stuff they never saw
in eastern Poland.

00:51:46.700 --> 00:51:54.050
So, they were, the girls were --
the perfumes and all that stuff

00:51:54.050 --> 00:51:59.940
and even though it was forbidden
the Jews always brought a camera.

00:51:59.940 --> 00:52:01.900
One of them, it was
in the warehouse,

00:52:01.900 --> 00:52:05.330
the Ukrainians didn't know
how to operate cameras

00:52:05.330 --> 00:52:08.120
but they wanted a picture
with their girlfriends.

00:52:08.120 --> 00:52:14.570 position:56%
So, they asked the Jew to take a
picture and you have the [inaudible]

00:52:14.570 --> 00:52:17.910
